text: "I Go Back" is a song written and recorded by American country music artist Kenny Chesney. It was released in May 2004 as the third single from his 2004 album When the Sun Goes Down. ==Music video== The music video was directed by Shaun Silva. It premiered on CMT on June 12, 2004. The video debuted at number 19 on CMT's Top 20 Countdown for the week of July 1, 2004. The video peaked at number 1 on CMT's Top Twenty Countdown for two consecutive weeks in August 2004. ==References== Category:2004 songs Category:Country songs Category:Kenny Chesney songs Category:BNA Records singles Category:Music videos directed by Shaun Silva
